    This page is the front‑facing website for a student‑led digital wellbeing campaign.
    It follows a clear narrative: introduce the problem of digital burnout,
    explain the warning signs, propose a simple reset plan, share student stories,
    showcase events and gallery content, and finally invite visitors to get involved.
    The design is intentionally simple and uses a calm colour palette defined in
    style.css. If you see only plain text when loading this file, make sure the
    accompanying style.css file is located in the same directory as this index.html.
  -->
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css" />
